Nuclear Data Inc bank lender agree extend secure loan agreement June 30 1987. The agreement cover 9.5 mln dlrs short term debt schedule expire February 28. Terms extension require Nuclear Data obtain replacement financing outside source June 30 said. If company unable fails achieve project operating result meantime require divest asset retire debt said. For nine month fiscal 1987 end November 30 1986 Nuclear Data report loss nine mln dlrs 4.98 dlrs share revenue 32.6 mln dlrs. Nuclear Data cite improvement print circuit board sale confident obtain replacement financing. In action Nuclear Data 1.25 mln dlrs reserve cover revaluation domestic medical inventory redirection U.S. medical sale efforts. The reserve take offset decline U.S. dollar Danish Kroner factor adversely affect sale Danish manufacture medical product U.S. market Nuclear Data said. Reuter 